UPDATE `quest_template` SET `QuestDescription`='$n, although we had hoped the Twilight''s Hammer''s operations in Silithus were slowing... we were, regrettably, mistaken.  Through continued forays against the cult, we have learned that an even darker power, the Abyssal Council, controls the Hammer through the arcane wind stones dotted amongst the cult''s camps.  Your next action, $n, will be against the Abyssal Council.$B$BSpeak with the craftsman Aurel Goldleaf, in the eastern section of Cenarion Hold.  Her skill will be needed for this next gambit.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `Id`=8331; -- Aurel Goldleaf
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `QuestDescription`='$n, Aurel Goldleaf thinks she''s found a way to summon and defeat a ruling member of the Abyssal Council!  Such a task will be dangerous, but you have earned great respect amongst the Cenarion Circle.  We know that if anyone can do it, you can.$B$BMay fortune go with you, $n.  Speak with Aurel when you are ready.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `Id`=8343; -- Goldleaf's Discovery
