UPDATE `quest_template` SET `RewardBonusMoney`=102300, `AllowableRaces`=33555378, `QuestDescription`='Darkness stirs, $n. A tragic event has transpired that none but the Timeless One could have foreseen. Soon your people will be gripped by anger and hatred. War is on the horizon.$B$BThe red dragonflight has done all that it can. What happens next is in the hands of the mortal races of Azeroth.$B$BRegrettably, your journey begins with anguish. A father has lost a child today. You must bear the grim news. Gather the armaments of Saurfang and return them to the elder Saurfang. \n', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `Id`=13242; -- Darkness Stirs
